<h1>Stream</h1>

<p>Opens a stream the to server.</p>

<p>Stream name: <code><%= @stream.name %></code></p>

<p>Broadcast from Rails console via: <code>Stream.find(<%= @stream.name.inspect %>).broadcast</code></p>

<p><%= link_to "Ping Stream", stream_pings_path(@stream), data: { "turbo-method": :post } %><p>

<h2>Stream</h2>
<%= turbo_stream_from @stream.name %>
